Repository License And Provenance Boundary

Copyright (c) 2015-2026 David J. Giacomin and David M. Levinson

This repository is a mixed research package. The license below applies only
to materials that the paper authors or repository maintainers have rights to
license, and it does not relicense excluded, public-agency, publisher, or
third-party source materials.

## Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International

Author-created repository documentation, package metadata, source-decision
notes, workbook profiles, and rights-cleared derived circuity/accessibility
workbook content and CSV exports are licensed under the Creative Commons
Attribution 4.0 International License (CC BY 4.0):

https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/

This includes author-created selection, cleaning, integration, workbook
organization, formulas, tabulation, summary measures, circuity/accessibility
calculations, and modernized CSV exports reflected in `data/derived_workbooks/`
and `data/csv_exports/`, only to the extent controlled by the paper authors or
repository maintainers.

## Materials Not Relicensed

This repository license does not apply to:

- Publication PDFs, proof PDFs, and publisher or repository copies under
  `paper/` or `documentation/nonfinal_paper_context/`.
- Raw Census/TIGER road-network GIS files, MSA boundary files, Census
  geography definitions, HPMS records, NHTS records, Urban Mobility Report
  source tables, INRIX or speed source records, public-agency source materials,
  and other source data used to construct the derived workbooks.
- Manuscript drafts, reviewer responses, LaTeX/build products, figure-only
  PDFs, vendor file-format structures, cited references, and other
  third-party materials.

## Software Boundary

No executable software, scripts, notebooks, model source code, ArcGIS/Network
Analyst scripts, or paper-specific runtime code are staged in this repository.
This root license therefore grants no separate software license.
